    <stitle>INTERNATIONAL&#174; VT 365 DIESEL ENGINE - ENGINE ELECTRICAL - Installation - Glow Plug Relay and Bracket
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="1">
        <title>Glow Plug Relay and Bracket</title>
        <figure id="f2351055" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figd09/D0918.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px" box="no"/>
            <caption>Figure 404. Glow plug relay terminals</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">To battery source</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">To ECM (X1 connector)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">To ECM (w/ fusible link) (X1 connector), glow plug harness busbars</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">To ground</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">Mounting bolts (2)</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Install glow plug relay onto its bracket. Install and tighten two mounting bolts.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">If removed, install bracket and three nuts to valve cover studs. Tighten nuts to the Special
                Torque Torque .
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect glow plug wire and 12-V power wire to top of glow plug relay. Tighten terminal
                nuts.
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Connect wiring harness connector to glow plug relay.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Reconnect batteries.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
